Heward is a Hero-power of bards and music, the creator of a legendary pipe organ artifact with many extraordinary powers. He dwells in an extraplanar nexus that connects many times and planes, guarded by nonmagical constructs of his own devising.
He is an ally of Zagyg, Murlynd, Keoghtom, Celestian, Fharlanghn, and others. 

